ects of binary evolution. Yet, our models provide a clear\npath for linking the final stages of massive stars to their post-explosion\nspectra at early times, and guiding future observational follow-up of\ntransients with facilities such as the Zwicky Transient Facility.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Nov 2018 18:01:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Nov 2018 11:29:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-23"}
