ulations. Furthermore, some general\nguidelines based on the analytical model are presented for optimization of the\ntransducer's dimensions. Finally, based on the guidelines, a new bidirectional\nSH0 wave piezoelectric transducer is proposed with very small beam divergence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Nov 2018 14:26:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Feb 2019 14:42:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-13"}
